Pre-built pim-daemon binaries are downloaded here by CI via
`scripts/fetch-daemon.sh`. Not committed to git — see .gitignore.

Expected filenames (Tauri 2 sidecar convention):
  pim-daemon-aarch64-apple-darwin
  pim-daemon-x86_64-apple-darwin
  pim-daemon-x86_64-pc-windows-msvc.exe
  pim-daemon-x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu
  pim-daemon-aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu
